hopobject.body: The National Gallery finaflex absolute mass As Nicky tells me: “I think probably the one remaining issue that would need to be addressed is the issue of culture within the combat arms. The infantry and armoured corps, just like the other cap badges [areas] of the Army prior to allowing women to serve, has been used to being an all-male club, and in lifting the ban, those cap badges will need to look long and hard at their culture and to identify how best to accommodate difference.”
